  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 425F.",
    "Cut the asparagus into 1-inch pieces and place on a baking sheet.",
    "Drizzle the asparagus with olive oil, sprinkle with salt and pepper, and roast in the oven for 12 minutes.",
    "Meanwhile, heat the sesame oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the minced garlic and ginger and cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the soy sauce, honey, and rice vinegar to the pan and stir to combine.",
    "Add the sesame seeds to the pan and stir to combine.",
    "Once the asparagus is done roasting, place it in a dolsot stone bowl.",
    "Pour the sauce from the pan over the asparagus.",
    "Serve immediately."
